 chevrolet detroit zone he was appointed plant manager chevrolet gear and axle one of the five plants he later acquired to cofound american axle and manufacturing in  dauch became vice president of manufacturing for volkswagen manufacturing of america where he managed the manufacturing facilities volkswagen westmoreland assembly the first volume automotive transplant in the united states dauch joined chrysler in april  as vice president of diversified operations where he helped reengineer their manufacturing systems establishing justintime material management systems and the three shift manufacturing vehicle assembly process dauch retired from chrysler in  as executive vice president of worldwide manufacturing american axle and manufacturingedit in  dauch headed an investment group that acquired five general motors parts plants in michigan and new york to form american axle and manufacturing it became a standalone tier one automotive supplier on march   american axle has become a publicly traded company on the new york stock exchange and has grown from its original five plants to  locations worldwide american driveedit dauch has written a book about his experiences called american drive how manufacturing will save our country  written with coauthor hank h cox the book was published in september  the book narrates the story of aam against the backdrop of nearly fifty years in the auto industry from americas glory days to its massive decline in the face of foreign competition the government bailouts battles with unions and the recent financial crisis deathedit dauch died on august   of cancer in his home in bloomfield hills michigan according to the oakland county medical examiners office american axle said in a statement our thoughts and prayers are with dick’s family and friends all of us have lost a great friend and leader awardsedit  automotive hall of fames industry leader of the year  michigan manufacturers association manufacturer of the year  crains detroit business newsmaker of the year  detroit news michiganian of the year  detroit regional chambers world trader of the year  wayne state university college of business administrations michigan executive of the year  ceo legend award from automation alley  shienming wu foundation manufacturing leadership award  aam ceo richard e dauch was named keynote speaker at automotive parts manufacturers association conference marketwatchcom june   referencesedit  kiska t  detroits powers  personalities momentum books isbn  retrieved    richard e dauch with dr jack troyanovich  passion for manufacturing society of manufacturing engineers isbn   a b httpnewsunspurdueeduhtmlmonthdauchalumnicenterhtml retrieved   httpwwwuwsemorgbloguwsemrichardedauchchairsunitedwayshtml united way women initiative celebrates success of first year retrieved   a b httpwwwnationalsummitorgspeakerdauchperspective retrieved   a b c american axle manufacturing  delivering power aamcom retrieved    american drive   company overview  american axle  manufacturing aamcom retrieved    a b american axle cofounder richard dauch dies of cancer at  theoaklandpresscom retrieved   authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerichardedaucholdid categories  births deathsamerican businesspeoplepeople from huron county ohiopurdue university alumnihidden categories articles with hcardswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version lan